            "detailed_description": "Project Ara - Crucible is a bullet hell type shoot’em’up featuring procedural content generation in addition to light RPG elements. Help Lethe Zelmiya, the forgetful wizard on her epic quest to graduate from the Myrellian Academy of Magic.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKey Features<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe enemy waves in the 5 stages of the Crucible are randomly generated and adapts to your skill level keeping the game challenging for novices and experts alike.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers can adjust the game's challenge rating to suit their abilities.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLevel up to gain powerful randomized feats to defeat your foes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLethe's Magic Runes alter her primary attacks in varied ways.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBullet Patterns contain no random elements to promote skill-based game play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSurvival Mode pits you against an endless gauntlet of enemies.",
